outhern California, Prof. Manji shuttles between New York and Los Angeles, using the culture of each city to inform the other. She also travels beyond both coasts to engage the global audience that she has built as a religious reformer, best-selling author, and award-winning filmmaker.\n<br/><br/>\nFor all her titles, Prof. Manji is an educator at heart. She started the Moral Courage Project at New York University, during which time she shared the stage with His Holiness the Dalai Lama,  Martin Luther King III and Christiane Amanpour. African by birth, Canadian by citizenship, American by immersion and universal by reach, Irshad Manji inspires new perspectives on success, significance, diversity and meaning in work.\";s:17:\"bottom-left-title\";s:5:\"Learn\";s:21:\"bottom-left-paragraph\";s:47:\"Irshad at the University of Southern California\";s:31:\"bottom-left-call-to-action-link\";s:86:\"https://communicationleadership.usc.edu/news/muslim-reformer-named-cclp-senior-fellow/\";s:32:\"bottom-left-call-to-action-image\";s:3:\"374\";s:19:\"bottom-middle-title\";s:4:\"Join\";s:23:\"bottom-middle-paragraph\";s:21:\"Irshad’s newsletter\";s:33:\"bottom-middle-call-to-action-link\";s:43:\"http://irshadmanji.com/join-newsletter-page\";s:34:\"bottom-middle-call-to-action-image\";s:3:\"145\";s:18:\"bottom-right-title\";s:4:\"Read\";s:22:\"bottom-right-paragraph\";s:16:\"Irshad’s books\";s:32:\"bottom-right-call-to-action-link\";s:34:\"http://irshadmanji.com/store/books\";s:33:\"bottom-right-call-to-action-image\";s:3:\"144\";}}'),(430,141,'_edit_last','1'),(431,141,'_edit_lock','1413209099:2'),(432,142,'_wp_attached_file','2014/09/nyu.jpg'),(433,142,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:100;s:6:\"height\";i:100;s:4:\"file\";s:15:\"2014/09/nyu.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:0:{}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";